<h1 id="-watch-request-">.watch(<code>request</code>)</h1>
<h3 id="purpose" permalink="purpose">Purpose</h3>
<p>This subscribes a client to publishCreate events for the model.  Any connections that are &quot;watching&quot; the model class will be automatically subscribed to new model instances that are created using the blueprint <code>create</code> method.</p>
